# Path to the Tesseract OCR binary on this machine.
# OPTIONAL: settings.py auto-detects Tesseract on the PATH and in the standard
# install folders, so you usually do not need to set this at all. Set it only if
# Tesseract is installed somewhere non-standard. A path that does not exist on this
# machine is ignored (auto-detection takes over), so a stale value can't break OCR.
#   macOS (Homebrew): /opt/homebrew/bin/tesseract
#   Linux:            /usr/bin/tesseract
#   Windows:          C:\Program Files\Tesseract-OCR\tesseract.exe



